text: Elise Estrada is the self-titled debut extended play (EP) by Canadian recording artist Elise Estrada. It was released on April 15, 2004.Elise Estrada (Explicit). Elise Estrada. 15 Apr 2004 == Track listing == ==References== Category:Elise Estrada albums Category:2004 debut EPs
